p = 5659, q = 5669

n = 32080871

$(n) = (5659- 1)*(5669- 1) = 32069544

e = 17

ed === 1 (mod $(n))

ed + kn === 1, n和e肯定是互质, 所以可以用exgcd求出来 d 和 k


计算出的密钥为：( n = 32080871, d =  24523769)

计算出的公钥为：( n = 32080871, e = 17)

## 测试：

假设原文为 20221011

令 m = 20221011 带入加密公式得：

 c = 31758592

再把c带入解密公式得：

m = 20221011

```c++
#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;
typedef long long LL;
​
LL exgcd(LL a, LL b, LL &d, LL &k)
{
    if(!b)
    {
        d = 1, k = 0;
        return a;
    }
    LL t = exgcd(b, a % b, k, d);
    k = k-a/b * d;
    return t;
}
​
LL qmi(int a, int b, LL p)
{
    LL res = 1;
    while(b)
    {
        if(b & 1) res = (LL)res * a % p;
        b >>= 1;
        a = (LL)a * a % p;
    }
    return res;
}
​
int main()
{
    LL e = 17,n = 32080871, eurl_n = 32069544;
    LL d, k;
    
    exgcd(e,eurl_n,d,k);
    //cout << "k:" << k << endl;
    cout << "计算出的私钥为";
    d = (d % eurl_n + eurl_n) % eurl_n;
    
    cout << "( " <<  n << ", " << d << " )\n";
    cout << "计算出的公钥为：";
    cout << "( " <<  n << ", " << e << " )\n\n";
    cout << "输入要加密的原文（小于n）:";
    
    LL m;
    cin >> m;
    LL c = qmi(m,e,n);
    
    cout << "密文为：" << c << "\n";
     
    cout << "解密测试：" << qmi(c, d, n);
    
    return 0;
}
```
